<script>
  function ga_screenview(){
    var emptyObject = new Object();
    emptyObject = ga_set_dimension(emptyObject);
    emptyObject.t = 'screenview';
    httpPostSend(emptyObject)
  }
  function ga_event(_category, _action, _label){ 
    var emptyObject = new Object();
    emptyObject = ga_set_dimension(emptyObject);
    emptyObject.t = 'event';
    emptyObject.ec = _category;
    emptyObject.ea = _action;
    emptyObject.el = _label;
    
    httpPostSend(emptyObject);
  }
  function ga_set_dimension(emptyObject){
    var tmpObject = new Object();
    for(var i=0; i<200; i++){
      var dimensionNum = 'dimension' + (i+1);
      var tmpDimensionNum = 'cd'+(i+1);
      if(getDataLayer(dimensionNum)!==undefined)tmpObject[tmpDimensionNum]= getDataLayer(dimensionNum);
      var metricNum = 'metric' + (i+1);
      var tmpMetricNum = 'cm' + (i+1);
      if(getDataLayer(metricNum)!==undefined)tmpObject[tmpMetricNum]= getDataLayer(metricNum);
    }
    tmpObject.aip = '1'
    tmpObject.ds = 'app'
    //tmpObject.tid = 'UA-124182386-3'
    tmpObject.tid = 'UA-115948787-1'
    
    getDataLayer('title')!== undefined ? tmpObject.cd = getDataLayer('title') : tmpObject.cd = document.title;
    getCookie('_ga_UserID')!== undefined ? tmpObject.uid = getCookie('_ga_UserID') : tmpObject.uid = getDataLayer('dimension2');
    getCookie('_ga_O2ID')!== undefined ? tmpObject.cd9 = getCookie('_ga_O2ID') : tmpObject.cd9 = getDataLayer('userId');
    getCookie('_ga_cid')!== undefined ? tmpObject.cid = getCookie('_ga_cid') : tmpObject.cid = getDataLayer('cid');
    getCookie('_ga_an')!== undefined ? tmpObject.an = getCookie('_ga_an') : tmpObject;
    getCookie('_ga_av')!== undefined ? tmpObject.av = getCookie('_ga_av') : tmpObject;
    getCookie('_ga_aid')!== undefined ? tmpObject.aid = getCookie('_ga_aid') : tmpObject;
    getCookie('_ga_ul')!== undefined ? tmpObject.ul = getCookie('_ga_ul') : tmpObject;
    getCookie('_ga_sr')!== undefined ? tmpObject.sr = getCookie('_ga_sr') : tmpObject;
    getCookie('_ga_idfa')!== undefined ? tmpObject.idfa = getCookie('_ga_idfa') : tmpObject;
    
    return tmpObject;  
  }
  function httpPostSend(ga_data){
    var parameters = 'v=1';
    for(var key in ga_data){
      parameters += '&';
      parameters += key;
      parameters += '=';
      parameters += ga_data[key];
    }
    var httpRequest = new XMLHttpRequest();
    var gaUrl = 'https://www.google-analytics.com/collect';
    httpRequest.open('POST',gaUrl,true);
    httpRequest.setRequestHeader('Content-type','application/x-www-form-urlencoded');
    httpRequest.onreadystatechange = postSend();
    httpRequest.send(parameters);
    function postSend(){
      if(httpRequest.readyState==4 && httpRequest.status ==200){}
    }
  }
  var getCookie = function(name){
    var i,x,y,ARRcookies = document.cookie.split(';');
    for(i=0;i<ARRcookies.length; i++){
      x=ARRcookies[i].substr(0,ARRcookies[i].indexOf('='));
      y=ARRcookies[i].substr(ARRcookies[i].indexOf('=')+1);
      x= x.replace(/^\s+|\s+$/g,"");
      if(x==name){
        return unescape(y);
      }
    }
  }
  function getDataLayer(data){
    var getValue = window.google_tag_manager["GTM-W3L5N4X"].dataLayer.get(data);
    var returnValue;
    if(getValue !== undefined){ returnValue = getValue}
    else{ returnValue = dataLayer[0][data]; }
    return returnValue;
  }

  window.onload = function(){
     ga_screenview();
  }
  
</script>
